description: The image shows a group of six people gathered in a circle, listening to a man who appears to be giving a presentation. The speaker is standing next to a small table with a laptop on it, the screen displaying some text, possibly "Mission/Marketing for AEC." They are in a room with light-colored walls. Behind the group is a small bar area with the "MGM Grand" logo visible. The group is casually dressed and appears to be engaged in the presentation. Some of them are seated on short stools. A water dispenser is visible on the bar behind them. Some people are wearing lanyards. There is a Puma bag on the bottom-left corner.
